Class Cycle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jfbuilds.tme1.program3.Cycle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bicycle, Tricycle, Unicycle

    public abstract class Cycle
extends java.lang.Object
    Cycle class represent a cycle device with subclasses of Unicycle, Bicycle, and Tricycle

    There are no fields associated for a cycle

    Static method to ride any cycle device (with possible upcasting) as well as a method to return related number of wheels on the device
